---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { config } from '../config';

const canonicalUrl = new URL('/privacy', Astro.url).href;
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Parksville Handyman"
  description="How we collect, use, and protect your information."
  canonicalUrl={canonicalUrl}
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8"><strong>Last updated:</strong> January 2025</p>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-8">
      <section>
        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>
          {config.businessName} ("we," "us," "our," or "Company") operates {config.businessName} ("Site"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website and submit inquiries.
        </p>
        <p>
          We comply with the <strong>Personal Information Protection and Electronic Documents Act (PIPEDA)</strong> and <strong>British Columbia's Personal Information Protection Act (BCPIPA)</strong>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

        <h3>A. Information You Provide</h3>
        <p>When you submit a quote request or contact form, we collect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your name</li>
          <li>Your phone number</li>
          <li>Your email address (if provided)</li>
          <li>The service you're interested in</li>
          <li>A description of your project or inquiry</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>B. Automatically Collected Information</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Log data:</strong> IP address, browser type, pages visited, time and date of visit</li>
          <li><strong>Cookies and tracking:</strong> Google Analytics 4 to understand how visitors use the Site</li>
          <li><strong>Device information:</strong> Device type, operating system, referral source</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>

        <p>We use the information you provide for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>To respond to your quote request or inquiry</li>
          <li>To send you updates about services (if you opt in)</li>
          <li>To improve our Site and services</li>
          <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
          <li>To detect and prevent fraud or abuse</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>Lead Sharing:</strong> When you submit a quote request, your information is shared with the local service provider operating under the {config.businessName} brand who will contact you to discuss your needs and provide an estimate.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>3. Cookies & Analytics</h2>

        <p>Our Site uses Google Analytics 4 to collect anonymized usage data. This helps us understand:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Which pages are most popular</li>
          <li>How long visitors stay on the Site</li>
          <li>How visitors navigate between pages</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>Your choices:</strong> You can opt out of Google Analytics by using the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank">Google Analytics Opt-Out Browser Add-on</a>.</p>

        <p>We use minimal cookies. Most tracking respects Do Not Track requests and does not identify you personally.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>

        <p>Our Site uses third-party services to function:</p>

        <ul>
          <li><strong>Resend (resend.com):</strong> Email delivery for quote requests</li>
          <li><strong>Cloudflare (cloudflare.com):</strong> CDN, DDoS protection, and hosting</li>
          <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> Website analytics and usage insights</li>
        </ul>

        <p>These services have their own privacy policies. We encourage you to review them. We do not share your information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>5. Data Security</h2>

        <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>HTTPS encryption on all pages</li>
          <li>Secure form submission with server-side validation</li>
          <li>Limited access to personal data (team members only)</li>
          <li>Regular security audits</li>
        </ul>

        <p>However, no security system is 100% impenetrable. We cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>

        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Access your information:</strong> Request what personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li><strong>Correct inaccuracies:</strong> Ask us to update or correct your information</li>
          <li><strong>Delete your information:</strong> Request deletion of your personal data (subject to legal holds)</li>
          <li><strong>Opt out of communications:</strong> Unsubscribe from marketing emails at any time</li>
        </ul>

        <p>To exercise these rights, email us at {config.email}.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>7. Data Retention</h2>

        <p>We retain your quote request information for up to 2 years to comply with our business and legal obligations. After that period, we delete or anonymize your data unless you have an active service agreement with us.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>

        <p>Our Site is not directed to individuals under 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If we learn we have collected data from a child under 13, we will delete it immediately.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>9. Policy Updates</h2>

        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date. Continued use of the Site after changes means you accept the updated policy.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>

        <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your information, contact us:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> {config.email}</li>
          <li><strong>Phone:</strong> {config.phone}</li>
        </ul>

        <p>If you have a privacy complaint, you can file a complaint with <strong>the Office of the Privacy Commissioner of Canada</strong> at <a href="https://www.priv.gc.ca" target="_blank">priv.gc.ca</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
